Detailed Description

A collection of resource data types within a package.

Followed by one or more ResTable_type and ResTable_typeSpec structures containing the entry values for each resource type.

◆ id

package.ResTable_package_header.id

If this is a base package, its ID.

Package IDs start at 1 (corresponding to the value of the package bits in a resource identifier). 0 means this is not a base package.
